@startuml SubmitPullRequest
left to right direction
skinparam style strictuml

actor Developer
actor GitHub

boundary "GitHub Interface" as GitHubUI
control "PR Handler" as PRHandler
entity "Pull Request" as PREntity

Developer --> GitHubUI : submit PR
GitHubUI --> GitHub : webhook trigger
GitHub --> PRHandler : receiveEvent()
PRHandler --> PREntity : analyzeCode()
PRHandler --> GitHub : postComments()
GitHub --> GitHubUI : display results

@enduml
